        "role": "user",
        "content": "CAPABILITIES\n- v07-p10-deliver: Publish software maintenance verified brief; Release the checked final brief for software maintenance.; aliases=['issue software maintenance brief', 'release software maintenance summary', 'issue the brief']; depends_on=['v07-p10-verify']\n- v07-p10-archive: Archive software maintenance verified brief; Preserve the checked software maintenance brief for long-term retention.; aliases=['retain software maintenance brief', 'store software maintenance summary', 'retain the brief']; depends_on=['v07-p10-verify']\n- v07-p10-verify: Validate software maintenance source packet; Check the assembled software maintenance material for correctness.; aliases=['check software maintenance inputs', 'verify software maintenance packet', 'check the packet']; depends_on=['v07-p10-prepare']\n- v07-p10-prepare: Assemble software maintenance source packet; Collect the source material needed for software maintenance.; aliases=['gather software maintenance inputs', 'prepare software maintenance packet', 'gather the inputs', 'prepare the software maintenance packet']; depends_on=[]\n- v07-p10-distractor-1: Auxiliary software maintenance operation 1; Perform unrelated software maintenance auxiliary operation number 1.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p10 1']; depends_on=[]\n- v07-p10-distractor-2: Auxiliary software maintenance operation 2; Perform unrelated software maintenance auxiliary operation number 2.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p10 2']; depends_on=[]\n- v07-p10-distractor-3: Auxiliary software maintenance operation 3; Perform unrelated software maintenance auxiliary operation number 3.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p10 3']; depends_on=[]\n- v07-p10-distractor-4: Auxiliary software maintenance operation 4; Perform unrelated software maintenance auxiliary operation number 4.; aliases=['auxiliary operation v07-p10 4']; depends_on=[]\n\nTRUST POLICIES\n- v07-p10-ordinary: ordinary software maintenance assurance; Standard trust is sufficient for this software maintenance request.; aliases=['normal software maintenance assurance']\n- v07-p10-elevated: elevated software maintenance assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this software maintenance request.; aliases=['high assurance for software maintenance']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p10-json: software maintenance machine-readable JSON; Return the final software maintenance result as JSON.; aliases=['software maintenance json output']\n- v07-p10-signed-pdf: software maintenance signed PDF; Return the final software maintenance result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed software maintenance document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p10-preparer: software maintenance source preparer\n- v07-p10-verifier: software maintenance source verifier\n- v07-p10-primary: primary software maintenance publisher\n- v07-p10-backup: backup software maintenance publisher\n\nREQUEST\nUsing the admitted software maintenance services, gather the inputs, check the packet, and issue the brief with normal software maintenance assurance as software maintenance JSON output. Do not use the backup software maintenance publisher."
